{"tid":1862582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我同你地講 我最愛就係共產黨  你班反共連登仔有咩問題","createTime":"2020-02-04T16:54:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T12:57:12.000Z","uid":170793,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6b5488306e31d6daf7e903329a76813087d7ed0","tid":1862582,"uid":170793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:54:06.000Z","msg":"最愛共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支持共產黨呢七十年嘅作為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n文革批撚鬥死班支那人  令班支那人自相殘殺<br />\n<br />\n大饑荒餓撚死幾千萬支那狗<br />\n<br />\n跟住唔比支那狗有自由  日日監控佢地  講錯野就拉 造謠<br />\n<br />\n令班支那狗日日生活係霧霾 毒空氣  毒奶粉 地溝油<br />\n<br />\n喂班支那狗食屎  班支那狗仲要日日感激國家感激黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根本虐待得支那狗最犀利嘅就係共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：超憎中國 超憎支那狗 但超級愛戴共產黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e39fee80e83a3d87da1649791610749a6dd431","tid":1862582,"uid":170793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:55:42.000Z","msg":"支持共產黨"},{"pid":"69d75a92d99ca56c9537883a021c488e7d499c90","tid":1862582,"uid":170793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:56:38.000Z","msg":"共產黨萬歲"},{"pid":"1775cdc215635d830c1d810e7ad4a191831967ff","tid":1862582,"uid":160675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T16:57:51.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"ee0726bb76d8e501d4876f985a538419e6efdd43","tid":1862582,"uid":256495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"reply